<m0>Volunteer work makes dream come true<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS .78 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .562 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
